The cache_v2 committed baseline is keyed by the HEAD mesh-tree OID and resolved committed_only, so it enumerates meshes via committed_mesh_names (HEAD tree only, excluding index and worktree); enumerating worktree or index meshes instead would bake untracked or uncommitted mesh files into a HEAD-keyed entry, making the warm-clean cache replay deleted or phantom meshes — a correctness contract the types do not enforce.
